{
  "texts": [
    "The convergence between DL and statistical methods in optimizing traffic management solutions was explored (Harrou et al. 2021).",
    "By drawing inspiration and insights from these prior works, the present research endeavors to contribute to the ever-evolving landscape of DL applications.",
    "This paradigm shift has the potential to reshape the extreme weather analysis (Chen, Zhang et al. 2020).",
    "An ensemble of deep learning methods were utilized to detect cyclones (Kumler-Bonfanti et al. 2020) using a twenty-year dataset of simulated data.",
    "Another convolutional neural network (CNN) architecture (Kim et al. 2017) was developed to accurately pinpoint severe occurrences, achieving a remarkable accuracy rate of 99.98%."
  ]
}